Perl Module Term-ProgressBar:

    Progress bar for things that take a while.

Description:

    A progress bar for things that take a while.  It looks like

      50% [=====     ]

    and is as long as the terminal.  Linear estimation of the time left
    for the process to run is available.

Modules & Classes:

    Term::ProgressBar - provide a progress meter on a standard terminal

Executables:

    *None*

Required Perl Version:

    5_005.62

Required Packages:

    Class-MethodMaker 1.02
    TermReadKey       2.14

Required Executables:

    *None*

